                <div class="profile-details">
                    <h3>Harsh Narayana</h3>
                    <p><strong>Batch:</strong> 2002</p>
                    <p> Indian programmer who is often considered to be "India's greatest coder</p>
                    
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="profile-card">
                <div class="profile-image" style="background-image: url('https://res.cloudinary.com/dhhe18dia/image/upload/v1750833425/vijay_bhaskar_v3s6up.jpg');"></div>
